# Cloudflare redirects. First match wins.
#
# 1) The overview page on this site moved from /docs/ to /overview/. A lot of
#    incoming links still point at the old path, so redirect it permanently.
#    These are exact-path rules, so they do not capture the /docs/<section>/*
#    sub-paths in (2), which go to the external docs site instead.
/docs   /overview/   301
/docs/  /overview/   301
#
# 2) The concept, getting-started, and overview reference docs moved to
#    docs.deepcausality.com. The splat (:splat) preserves the path tail,
#    including its trailing slash, e.g. /docs/concepts/causaloid/ maps to
#    https://docs.deepcausality.com/concepts/causaloid/.
/docs/concepts/*        https://docs.deepcausality.com/concepts/:splat        301
/docs/getting-started/* https://docs.deepcausality.com/getting-started/:splat 301
/docs/overview/*        https://docs.deepcausality.com/overview/:splat        301
